  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126200/extras/165068ea5beae6f30d5877222f96bf22.avif?t=1744074278\" width=416 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Isle of Pochimoon</strong> <br>is a Bullet Heaven game that blends <strong>life-simulation</strong> elements, including a building system, crafting, selling products at a convenience store, fishing, taming Pochimoon, and Pochimoon Fusion a unique mechanic where you can fuse two distinct Pochimoon to create an entirely new one, to help you in combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Heaven</strong><br>Survive as long as you can! Experiment with different builds by taming Pochimoon and fusing them to aid your survival. Gather materials, sell them at the convenience store, and brace yourself—the difficulty escalates over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Construct Buildings</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>construct essential buildings to meet your needs. These include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Woodcutter</strong> to produce wood,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Mine</strong> to gather metal,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Fusion Lab</strong> to fuse Pochimoon,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A<strong> Soil </strong>to plant crops,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And a <strong>Workshop</strong> to craft items.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126200/extras/165068ea5beae6f30d5877222f96bf22.avif?t=1744074278\" width=416 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Isle of Pochimoon</strong> <br>is a Bullet Heaven game that blends <strong>life-simulation</strong> elements, including a building system, crafting, selling products at a convenience store, fishing, taming Pochimoon, and Pochimoon Fusion a unique mechanic where you can fuse two distinct Pochimoon to create an entirely new one, to help you in combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Heaven</strong><br>Survive as long as you can! Experiment with different builds by taming Pochimoon and fusing them to aid your survival. Gather materials, sell them at the convenience store, and brace yourself—the difficulty escalates over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Construct Buildings</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>construct essential buildings to meet your needs. These include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Woodcutter</strong> to produce wood,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Mine</strong> to gather metal,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Fusion Lab</strong> to fuse Pochimoon,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A<strong> Soil </strong>to plant crops,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And a <strong>Workshop</strong> to craft items.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
